What will this code log?

```js
const user = {
  firstName: 'Alice',
  lastName: 'Brown',
  fullName: function() {
    return this.firstName + ' ' + this.lastName;
  }
};

console.log(user.fullName());
```

Find the bug in this code:

```js
const car = {
  brand: 'Toyota',
  model: 'Corolla',
  getDetails: () => `${this.brand} ${this.model}`
};

console.log(car.getDetails());
```
